&lt;h2&gt;About the Role&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;0&quot; data-end=&quot;45&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;0&quot; data-end=&quot;45&quot;&gt;Senior AI Engineer – Generative AI &amp;amp; LLMs&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
