&lt;p data-start=&quot;489&quot; data-end=&quot;792&quot;&gt;This role is ideal for someone with strong engineering depth who can bridge research and production—building robust AI platforms, optimizing LLM workflows, and delivering high-impact solutions across forecasting, route optimization, anomaly detection, predictive maintenance, and intelligent automation.&lt;/p&gt;
