&lt;h2&gt;About Neon -- Our Computational Knowledge Graph Platform&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Neon is Avathon&#39;s proprietary Computational Knowledge Graph (CKG) platform that combines:&lt;/p&gt;
