&lt;p&gt;This is a player-coach role designed for a high-performing enterprise sales leader who combines exceptional individual execution with the ability to build and scale winning teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will personally own and close transformational enterprise deals while leading a team of 2–3 Account Executives focused on penetrating strategic accounts and acquiring new logos.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate brings a strong network of executive relationships, excels at consultative and value-based selling, and has a demonstrated track record of creating opportunities, navigating complex buying processes, and consistently exceeding ambitious revenue targets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute Avathon&#39;s Energy growth strategy across Oil &amp;amp; Gas, Utilities, Power Generation, Renewables, and Energy Infrastructure.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify, prioritize, and penetrate the industry&#39;s largest target accounts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish trusted advisor relationships with senior executives and operational leaders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build, lead, and mentor a team of Account Executives and Sr. Account Executives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create and drive executive engagement strategies that lead to transformational enterprise opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead complex, multi-stakeholder sales cycles from initial engagement through contract execution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build compelling business cases around operational improvement, asset optimization, supply chain resilience, production efficiency, reliability, and autonomous operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with Avathon&#39;s executive leadership, product, strategy, and forward deployed engineering teams to shape customer-specific transformation roadmaps.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop strategic partnerships that position Avathon as a long-term AI platform provider across multiple operational domains.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent Avathon at industry events, executive forums, and board-level customer engagements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
